data.description: Welcome to your dream home! Nestled in a cozy and conveniently located neighborhood, this enchanting property offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and elegance. Step inside this charming abode to a bright, beautiful kitchen adorned with stainless steel appliances, ample storage, and gorgeous granite countertops and island that seamlessly connects with living space, offering an open concept floorplan perfect for spending time together and hosting. Enjoy the quiet privacy of the primary suite, tucked away in the back of the home. Relax and unwind in your personal sanctuary featuring a lavish garden tub, offering a tranquil retreat after a long day! Two additional cozy bedrooms provide versatility as bedrooms or space for a home office, ensuring both comfort and functionality. Beyond the walls, discover the expansive backyard, offering plenty of space to host large gatherings, towering playsets, eager pets ready to explore and exercise and even room for custom landscaping or a home grown vegetable garden. The possibilities for your dream oasis are endless! Within the neighborhood, indulge in the community amenities including a children's playground, and lively neighborhood pool, perfect for creating lasting memories and fostering connections with neighbors. Beyond the neighborhood, convenience is at your fingertips. Enjoy quick commute to Lackland AFB, easy access to Potranco HEB, Chick-fil-A, Starbucks, and plenty of entertainment options.
